{"tid":1943330,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"西班牙向華購逾4.3億醫療物資","createTime":"2020-03-25T15:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T15:42:13.000Z","uid":104804,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"444f9b0a39a25becde679a33f98a986d30eab865","tid":1943330,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T15:18:28.000Z","msg":"西班牙當局公佈，過去24小時新增738死，累計死亡人數增至3434人，成為繼意大利後，死亡人數超越中國的國家。確診人數則累積至47,610人。<br />\n<br />\n另外，西班牙衞生部長伊利亞（Salvador Illa）周三公佈，與中國簽署價值4.32億歐元（36億港元）的購買醫療用品合約，包括5500萬個口罩、550萬個快速測試套件、950個呼吸機和1,100萬對醫療手套。<br />\n<br />\n中國真係最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ce4ea01b2b6c6ff818946a1b15c638f8792e70","tid":1943330,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T15:19:06.000Z","msg":"睇下捷克d testing kit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b8cf1ea989bda9d98935faa9fb8bc4a23d776b","tid":1943330,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T15:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/2/24/Tvb_hail_commie_winner.png/revision/latest?cb=20181215123622\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F2%2F24%2FTvb_hail_commie_winner.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20181215123622&h=9521c68c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfaa611fdafe5bb6e5ca531cb481bf54504a8c25","tid":1943330,"uid":68111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T15:24:08.000Z","msg":"仲要俾埋機會中國做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57b107aa440468ce1b05ca693436022c93c1cea","tid":1943330,"uid":322195,"like":0,"dis